data.description: Now on the market is a 2,067 SqFt Colonial Home, a 3 bedroom Middleville property sitting waterside on the West Canda Creek while also residing on .42 of an acre! This home offers a quality interior & exterior condition: with spacious rooms throughout the entirety of the interior layout including the large living room   with fireplace, the kitchen with an eat-in island, and formal dining room. The 3 bedrooms are also large in- size to provide both quality & comfortability, as well as the ability to design all of the rooms at the homeowners' pleasure. The home holds 1.5 bathrooms, with a half bathroom on the 1st level & a full bathroom on the 2nd floor. Laundry hookups can be found in the basement, a space suitable for storage while also having renovation potential. Additional storage space can also be found in the attic. Additional exterior amenities of the property include a front porch as well as surrounding yard-space to utilize. This property has been removed from the flood zone as of August 31,2021!!
